{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_08_01",
  "title": "伊吹渚 1話 恋する少女、伊吹渚",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "私をヒロインにした恋愛ゲーム……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A romance game… with me as the heroine?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ゲーム会社の持ち込み企画で、星見プロのアイドルを\n使ったゲームを作ることになったんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A game company brought us a proposal to make a game\nfeaturing Hoshimi Production idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.3333333652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "それってもしかして……前に怜ちゃんを\nモデルに作ったゲームのことですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you mean the game that\nRei-chan featured as a model before!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.1797965209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "察しがいいな、正解だ。前回が好評だったみたいでな\n今回はその第二弾ってことらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re sharp. That’s right. Apparently the last one was well-received.\nIt seems this time they’re making a second installment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.3666672707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "先方は「今回はぜひ伊吹さんに」と\nおっしゃっているんだが……どうだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They said‚ “We’d really like Ibuki-san as a model this time‚”\nbut… what do you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.100000604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "ぜひやらせて下さい！　私があのゲームの\nヒロインになれるなんて……とっても嬉しいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’d love to do it! I can’t believe I get to be\nthe heroine of that game… I’m so happy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.456644392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "私、もう何回もプレイしてて……\n怜ちゃん、すっごく可愛いんですよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve played it so many times already…\nYou know‚ Rei-chan is so cute!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.4899777253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "一人で全部のエンドをクリアした後は、月ストの\nみんなに順番にプレイしてもらって、横で眺めてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After I cleared all the endings by myself‚ I made all the girls in Moon Tempest\nto play it in order and watched from the side.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3233110587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そういう楽しみ方もあるんだな\nみんな、どんな反応だったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s another way to enjoy it.\nWhat were their reactions like?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.800000604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 60.1712486903
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんとすずちゃんは、怜ちゃんのセリフとか\n仕草の一つ一つに分かりやすく反応してましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan and Suzu-chan had really obvious reactions\nto each and every one of Rei-chan’s lines and gestures.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.4545820236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "特に怜ちゃんがデレた時なんて\n二人とも顔を真っ赤にしちゃって……可愛かったな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Especially when Rei-chan blushed‚\ntheir faces turned bright red too… It was so cute~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.4545820236,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11495.417976400006,
          "startTime": 82.95
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_night",
      "startTime": 78.2045820236
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それだけプレイしてくれているなら話は早いな\nこの書類を見てくれるか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you’ve played it that much‚ then this will be quick.\nWould you take a look at these documents?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.866668288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "これは……アンケートですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are these… questionnaires?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7025200049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ゲームのシナリオを作るにあたって\n出来るだけ書いてみてほしいそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They want you to fill them out as much as you can\nfor references to make the game scenario.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7000041645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "ええと、私の恋愛観に、あとはゲーム内で\nやってみたいシチュエーション……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ my views on love and…\nsituations I’d like to try in the game…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.2623397827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "これ……本当に私が書いていいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it really okay for me to write this…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.2290074666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんだ。思いつくまま書いてみてくれ\n内容が充実している方が、先方も考えやすいからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. Just write whatever comes to mind.\nThe more detailed the content‚ the easier it will be for them to come up with ideas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.0333390237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "私の希望がゲームに……！？　わー、嬉しいです！\nありがとうございます、いっっっぱい考えてきますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My suggestions will be in the game…!? Wow~‚ I’m so happy!\nThank you very much‚ I’ll come up with lots of ideas!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.8937019507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――後日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Several days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.9603686173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.1270383358
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.1270383358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、アンケートを書いて\nきたので、確認してもらえますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ I finished writing the questionnaires‚\ncould you check them for me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.1270383358,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2933.3333332999982,
          "startTime": 130.0603716691
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3672.963190100006,
          "startTime": 130.8000015259
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4372.963190099995,
          "startTime": 131.5000015259
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6772.9631901,
          "startTime": 133.9000015259
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……凄い量だな。内容も具体的だし、ゲームに出てくる\n選択肢のアイデア出しまでしてくれたのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…This is quite a lot. The content is detailed‚ and you’ve even included\nideas for choices.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.2333420755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.2545664787
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "アンケートを書く時、沙季ちゃんの資料を\n参考にさせてもらったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I was writing the questionnaires‚ I used Saki-san’s materials\nas reference.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.787899812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　沙季の資料……？　どういうことだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm? Saki’s materials…? What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.0212331454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんのゲーム攻略のために\n沙季ちゃんが資料を作ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki-chan made some materials\nto help people to beat Rei-chan’s game.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.7566525936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 153.4399859269
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃんにもゲームをプレイしてもらったんですけど\n「え、そっち！？」って思う選択肢を何回も選んでて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I madeSaki-chan play the game too‚\nand she kept choosing options that made me think‚ “Eh‚ seriously!?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.6899859269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "最初はバッドエンドになったんです\nでも、そこで沙季ちゃんのスイッチが入って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and at first she got the bad ending.\nHowever‚ that flipped Saki-chan's switch…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.5899828752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
